flowRoot.flowPara: GNOME.Asia Summit is an annual conference of the GNOME desktop technology and free software/open source held in Asian countries. GNOME.Asia Summit 2015 will be held by GNU/Linux Bogor (GLiB) and Faculty of Computer Science, Universitas Indonesia (Fasilkom UI). There will be workshops, presentations and Lightning Talks with the target number of participants up to 500 peoples from the students and professionals.
